#. JWDk5
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:337
msgctxt "pastespecial|extended_tip|text"
msgid "Inserts cells containing text."
msgstr "Cuireann sé cealla ina bhfuil téacs isteach."

