#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:394
msgctxt "pastespecial|extended_tip|comments"
msgid "Inserts comments that are attached to cells. If you want to add the comments to the existing cell content, select the \"Add\" operation."
msgstr "Cuireann sé seo tráchtanna atá ceangailte le cealla isteach. Más mian leat na tráchtanna a chur leis an ábhar atá sa chealla cheana féin, roghnaigh an oibríocht \"Cuir leis\"."

#. 5n5r7
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:405
msgctxt "pastespecial|objects"
msgid "Objects"
msgstr "Réada"

#. DZsnr
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:413
msgctxt "pastespecial|extended_tip|objects"
msgid "Inserts objects contained within the selected cell range. These can be OLE objects, chart objects, or drawing objects."
msgstr "Cuireann sé seo réada atá laistigh den raon cealla roghnaithe isteach. Is féidir leo seo a bheith ina réada OLE, ina réada cairte, nó ina réada líníochta."

#. 2wYuG
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:424
msgctxt "pastespecial|formulas"
msgid "Formulas"
msgstr "Foirmlí"

#. Na5Ba
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:432
msgctxt "pastespecial|extended_tip|formulas"
msgid "Inserts cells containing formulae."
msgstr "Cuireann sé cealla ina bhfuil foirmlí isteach."

#. UtpWA
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:447
msgctxt "pastespecial|label1"
msgid "Paste"
msgstr "Greamaigh"

#. SKs5y
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:478
msgctxt "pastespecial|no_shift"
msgid "Don't shift"
msgstr "Ná bog"

#. q3Xv3
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:487
msgctxt "pastespecial|extended_tip|no_shift"
msgid "Inserted cells replace the target cells."
msgstr "Cuireann cealla curtha isteach na cealla sprice in ionad na gcealla sprice."

#. 4hD8A
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:499
msgctxt "pastespecial|move_down"
msgid "Down"
msgstr "Síos"

#. BNALN
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:508
msgctxt "pastespecial|extended_tip|move_down"
msgid "Target cells are shifted downward when you insert cells from the clipboard."
msgstr "Bogtar cealla sprice síos nuair a chuireann tú cealla isteach ón ngearrthaisce."

#. Psyof
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:520
msgctxt "pastespecial|move_right"
msgid "Right"
msgstr "Ar dheis"

#. GEFe7
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:529
msgctxt "pastespecial|extended_tip|move_right"
msgid "Target cells are shifted to the right when you insert cells from the clipboard."
msgstr "Bogtar cealla sprice ar dheis nuair a chuireann tú cealla isteach ón ngearrthaisce."

#. fzYTm
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:545
msgctxt "pastespecial|label4"
msgid "Shift Cells"
msgstr "Bog Cealla"

#. JXJTf
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:589
msgctxt "pastespecial|link"
msgid "As Link"
msgstr "Mar Nasc"

#. Bg9dc
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:597
msgctxt "pastespecial|extended_tip|link"
msgid "Inserts the cell range as a link, so that changes made to the cells in the source file are updated in the target file. To ensure that changes made to empty cells in the source file are updated in the target file, ensure that the \"Paste All\" option is also selected."
msgstr "Cuireann sé seo an raon cealla isteach mar nasc, ionas go ndéantar athruithe a dhéantar ar na cealla sa chomhad foinse a nuashonrú sa chomhad sprice. Chun a chinntiú go ndéantar athruithe a dhéantar ar chealla folamha sa chomhad foinse a nuashonrú sa chomhad sprice, cinntigh go bhfuil an rogha \"Greamaigh Gach Rud\" roghnaithe freisin."

#. 7yzbi
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:608
msgctxt "pastespecial|transpose"
msgid "Transpose"
msgstr "Traschur"

#. P3eE4
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:616
msgctxt "pastespecial|extended_tip|transpose"
msgid "The rows of the range in the clipboard are pasted to become columns of the output range. The columns of the range in the clipboard are pasted to become rows."
msgstr "Greamaítear sraitheanna an raoin sa ghearrthaisce chun colúin den raon aschuir a dhéanamh díobh. Greamaítear colúin an raoin sa ghearrthaisce chun sraitheanna a dhéanamh díobh."

#. 3VcAr
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:627
msgctxt "pastespecial|skip_empty"
msgid "Skip empty cells"
msgstr "Seachain cealla folamha"

#. BodqB
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:631
msgctxt "pastespecial|skip_empty"
msgid "If enabled, blank cells in source will not override the target."
msgstr "Leis seo, ní sháróidh cealla folmha san fhoinse an sprioc."

#. u2Cms
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:636
msgctxt "pastespecial|extended_tip|skip_empty"
msgid "Empty cells from the clipboard do not replace target cells. If you use this option in conjunction with the \"Multiply\" or the \"Divide\" operation, the operation is not applied to the target cell of an empty cell in the clipboard."
msgstr "Ní chuirtear cealla folamha ón ngearrthaisce in ionad na gcealla sprice. Mura n-úsáideann tú an rogha seo i gcomhar leis an oibríocht \"Iolraigh\" nó \"Roinn\", ní chuirtear an oibríocht i bhfeidhm ar chill sprice cille folamha sa ghearrthaisce."

#. jTFAJ
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:651
