msgstr "Roghanna"

#. ekYg5
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:682
msgctxt "pastespecial|none"
msgid "None"
msgstr "Dada"

#. 7GKDG
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:691
msgctxt "pastespecial|extended_tip|none"
msgid "Does not apply an operation when you insert the cell range from the clipboard. The contents of the clipboard will replace existing cell contents."
msgstr "Ní chuireann sé seo oibríocht i bhfeidhm nuair a chuireann tú an raon cealla isteach ón ngearrthaisce. Cuirfear ábhar an ghearrthaisce in ionad ábhar na gcealla atá ann cheana féin."

#. QhQnq
#: sc/uiconfig/scalc/ui/pastespecial.ui:703
msgctxt "pastespecial|add"
msgid "Add"
msgstr "Cuir leis"

